<item>
            <title>[LU-17831] improve time taken to discard pages under a lock</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17831</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A topic raised at the LUG hackathon is the time it takes to discard pages under a DLMlock when cancelling that lock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This can be extremely time consuming some times.&#160; A quick investigation shows a few ways to improve this and I&apos;ll capture them here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
